        <div class="text-box--species-media">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關影片
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHzoIF02l74">游動中的飯島氏海蛇</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X70hRsSMuEk">到水面呼吸的飯島氏海蛇</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.naturefootage.com/video_clips/NZ36_047">穿梭於珊瑚間的飯島氏海蛇 </a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.naturefootage.com/video_clips/NZ36_046">穿梭於珊瑚間的飯島氏海蛇(近拍)</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
