                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.dcview.com/article.php?a=VWhSNlAxVmc%253D">與海蛇共舞 - 取自 <span lang="en-US">DC View</span> 達人部落格</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-box-container text-box-container-info">
        <div class="text-box--species">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    家族
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    眼鏡蛇科, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/cgi-bin/res.pl?keyword=Hydrophiidae&offset=0">海蛇亞科</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    最大體長
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    85 cm
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    台灣棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Island,_Taiwan">綠島</a> 及 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orchid_Island">蘭嶼</a> 周圍
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    世界棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    中國，台灣，菲律賓，日本 (琉球群島)，印度尼西亞，菲律賓及摩鹿加群島，北至日本，南至薩摩亞群島的西太平洋地區。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    外觀描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    Small snake; total length up to 85 cm. There are 15-19 (17-19 at mid-body) rows of scales, which are smooth and imbricated, and there is a row of large hexagonal scales along the vertebral line. Head is small, cuboidal, and not distinct from neck; body is moderately stout and highly compressed laterally; tail is laterally compressed, sides with vertically elongated scales. Nostril (with a lid) faces upward. Eye is medium-sized. Fangs are degenerated. There are 2 prefrontals and no internasals or loreals. Head is black and marked with a cross band of yellow to orange anterior to eyes, extending backward and downward to the base of jaw. Body and tail are yellow to orange, encircled by black, wave-edged bands; the black band is slightly broader than or similar to the yellow-orange one in width. Anal scale is divided and subcaudals are paired.

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    生態描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text"> 	
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        此日夜雙行的蛇種居住於珊瑚礁及佈滿岩石的海底。為胎生，母體一次大約會產下兩隻仔蛇。
                    </div>
                    牠們唯一的食物來源為魚卵：「牠們利用硬化的吻部鱗片將魚卵由岩石上刮起，並利用鼻尖的尖刺挖起魚卵。牠們的顎部肌肉組織是很獨特的，毒牙較小，大概是由於他們需要利用吸力才能將魚卵吸入嘴裡。」　(<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://scienceblogs.com/tetrapodzoology/2007/06/tet_zoo_picture_of_the_day_15.php">資料來源</a>) 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    學名與俗名
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>Emydocephalus</i></span>: 源自於希臘文 <span lang="en-US"><i>emys</i></span> = 烏龜的，<span lang="en-US"><i>cephale</i></span> = 頭，指出此類蛇種的特殊頭形；
                    </div>
                    ijimae = 為紀念日本東京大學理科飯島教授而命名。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關連結
                </div>
                <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species" lang="en-US">
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://reptile-database.reptarium.cz/species.php?genus=Emydocephalus&species=ijimae">Reptile Database</a></li>
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sea_snake">Wikipedia - Sea Snakes</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="translator-name">翻譯:周信甫</div>

        </div>
    </div>

